{"tid":1011251,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"其實皇馬今次唔贏先奇怪","createTime":"2019-02-06T15:25:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-07T02:52:01.000Z","uid":90515,"like":29,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"def0c7d06de77baf30fc24cf15d1073a26877783","tid":1011251,"uid":90515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T15:25:36.000Z","msg":"皇馬出到最已陣，上場贏3粒<br />\n<br />\n新人雲尼素斯 馬利安奴愈踢愈好<br />\n無左淤血之後嘅賓斯馬大爆發，今季各項賽事入波只差阿朗1球<br />\n換左教練之後戰術合理兼狀態回勇<br />\n<br />\n反觀巴塞近況狀態差，踢到一舊屎咁，和華倫西亞都係靠好彩<br />\n<br />\n美斯傷傷地<br />\n丹比利無得出<br />\n阿蘇年紀大<br />\n佐迪艾巴 碧基chur盡<br />\n司利臣傷<br />\n烏迪迪連手術都未做<br />\n<br />\n理性預測今晚皇馬贏巴塞2到3粒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e843553026ae5671efac723a93959e0c06a9a1c4","tid":1011251,"uid":44285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T15:26:38.000Z","msg":"agger"},{"pid":"c41b247e135db4a3bdee80e64e76dccbd2d58eb0","tid":1011251,"uid":81273,"like":0,"dislike":21,"score":-21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T15:28:41.000Z","msg":"最強陣下話<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/pig2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1aa4fc40f3c8e9e6958850f24c0cebba5c89fe3a","tid":1011251,"uid":34419,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T15:29:43.000Z","msg":"合理 無美斯嘅巴塞=<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n依家皇馬個個上晒力 贏巴塞就一定 睇下係大炒456粒 定小勝3粒啫"},{"pid":"24cc9d5552d09c05c3dcdec431d9fe36629012b3","tid":1011251,"uid":1790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T16:21:54.000Z","msg":"合埋眼都知呢場3:7波"},{"pid":"0370429282d3112662890e0abc965410fec1d37e","tid":1011251,"uid":37197,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T16:22:42.000Z","msg":"馬里安奴仲傷緊喎"},{"pid":"c6f30c618f16255f7c5b581ee8a9233fa9176bfa","tid":1011251,"uid":33036,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0370429282d3112662890e0abc965410fec1d37e","tid":1011251,"uid":371